-- =============================================================================
-- SkillJewels: Gem-based spell learning system (Eluna)
-- =============================================================================
-- Generated by 02_generate_skill_jewels.py from skill_jewels_template.lua.template.
-- Do not edit this file directly. Edit the template or generator instead.
--
-- Real Spell Approach:
--   Gems teach REAL vanilla spells. Same-class gems are blocked at socket
--   time and skipped during sync. This guarantees all gem spells are
--   cross-class, making RemoveSpell always safe.
--
-- Why this works:
--   - A mage can never naturally learn Bloodthirst
--   - If the mage has Bloodthirst, it came from a gem
--   - RemoveSpell(Bloodthirst) is always safe for a mage
--   - Same-class gems are blocked, so this is guaranteed
--
-- Detection method:
--   - ON_LOGIN (event 3): full scan of equipped items
--   - ON_EQUIP (event 29): immediate rescan on equip
--   - ON_LEVEL_CHANGE (event 13): rescan to upgrade ranks
--   - Packet hooks: delayed rescan on unequip/socketing
-- =============================================================================

-- =============================================================================
-- CONFIGURATION
-- =============================================================================

